article_text:
A wreck on Highway 19 North has sent at least three people to the hospital Saturday evening.

It happened around 9 o'clock Saturday night just past the Newton County line. Family of one of the people injured says her parents were taken to the hospital, but they do not have life threatening injuries. There is no word on how badly injured the third person was.
